For Nicola, and other winemakers like him, this environmental change has existential consequences; it threatens his livelihood. “Wildfire” patiently observes Nicola in this affective state of anxiety—as the wildfire grows within him—as he’s forced to alter the course of his harvest in real time. Directed by Andree Ljutica.

programme.desc: In this very special episode of Operation Repo, it's the 36 hours that change everything. When Matt, Froy, and Lyndah go on a routine repo gone violently wrong, the bonds that connect the Pizarro family may be torn apart forever.

programme.title: Operation Repo
programme.desc: First, Lou and Sonia make their way to a home in the hills to clean a germaphobe of his car. Then, it's Matt and Froy's big repo. Having left the company to start their own, they head out after a high-end exotic car from outside a mansion. And finally, Lou, Lyndah, and Lou's cousin Rob drive out to a used car lot to pick up a few cars, but the owner has been hurt by the economy and now he's ready to do the hurting.

programme.title: Operation Repo
programme.desc: First, Lou and Sonia have an order for a Jaguar behind a retail outlet center, but will the loaders let their precious car be loaded up without a fight? Then, Matt and Froy find themselves amidst a lover's quarrel when a disgruntled wife reveals that she stopped payment on her car because of her cheating husband. And finally, a debtor is nowhere to be found when Lou, Lyndah, and Rob head out to a seemingly quiet neighborhood. The silence is broken when the debtor finally shows up in another vehicle with bang!

programme.title: Operation Repo
programme.desc: First, Matt and Froy end up on one of the weirdest repo's they've ever encountered when a white cargo van unleashes a wave of workers. Then, Lou, Sonia, and Rob go green when they find they learn the Mercedes Benz they are after has been converted to run on biodiesel. And finally, Matt and Froy can't seem to get a word in edgewise when they encounter a shrieking girl and her biker boyfriend who claim their Mercedes was paid in full. Little do our guys know that she was right all along.

programme.title: Operation Repo
programme.desc: Matt and Froy's business hits another snag when a gang of bat-wielding partiers keeps them away from a car and a paycheck. Then, Lou and Sonia wind up in the crosshairs when they attempt to repo a car from a man who appears to be a federal agent. And, with Matt and Froy's business in a complete shambles, they go to work in the only place that can save them Tijuana.

programme.title: Operation Repo
programme.desc: Matt and Froy continue their risky run in Tijuana, confronting a strip club owner who keeps a tight grip on his vehicle and his employees. Then, Lou and Cousin Rob are in a case of he said- she said when a seductive young debtor calls in the police with claims of some inappropriate behavior. Finally, the whole Pizarro family heads to an illegal street race to get their just desserts from the man who had previously hit Lyndah with his truck, but at what cost does revenge come?

programme.title: Operation Repo
programme.desc: Lou and his cousin Rob face trouble on the job when a debtor makes shocking claims to police about the newest member of the Pizarro clan. Plus, will a repossession from a well-connected socialite end with Matt and Froy riding into the sunset, or is somebody going to end up locked in a Mexican prison?

programme.title: Operation Repo
programme.desc: After Froy bails him out from a Tijuana prison, Matt is on the warpath, and somebody needs to pay. Is this just the end of their business, or is it also the end of their friendship? Then, Lou and Sonia get an order for a typical vehicle repossession. There's only one problem: it belongs to somebody who is like family to them.

programme.title: Operation Repo
programme.desc: The repo team is back! This week, the team confronts a shady import/export warehouse filled with unpaid-for cars, a pair of reckless rodeo gals, and a cunning team of car thieves who don't even think twice before running off with the team's truck.

programme.title: Operation Repo
programme.desc: After recovering their stolen truck, the reunited repo team is on pins and needles to hold their shaky alliance together.

programme.title: Operation Repo

programme.title: Operation Repo

programme.title: Operation Repo
programme.desc: Armed with the belief that he is now co-owner of the business, Matt starts making some big business calls - is this the beginning of a new chapter for the team, or the beginning of its undoing?

programme.title: La Mujer Perfecta
programme.desc: En este capitulo de esta apasionante historia de amores que se entrecruzan, luego de que Polanco le exige a Minerva que reincorpore a su puesto de trabajo a Micaela y pida disculpas delante de todo el personal, le pide a su chofer, Hinojosa que la lleve hasta su casa. Alli, Minerva e Hinojosa mantienen una conversacion en privado. Hinojosa le hace entender que ella es importante para el, y Minerva, que se siente mal por la actitud despectiva de Polanco; asi pues, ella se entrega a los brazos de Hinojosa. Por otro lado Nella consigue pasar la tarde con Saturno en su cama, mientras Estrella sigue sonando con la salida que hicieron juntos, el profesor Saturno y ella ¿Que pasara con esta relacion? ¿Saturno jugara a estar con Nella y con Estrella al mismo tiempo?

programme.title: Natalia del Mar
programme.desc: Patricia pide perdon, ella no queria que eso pasara y ahora todos corren peligro de muerte. Regina se siente ansiosa porque esta noche debuta como cantante en la discoteca del resort y le dice a su hermana que cuando cobre el primer sueldo la va a llevar a un medico para que se cure de su tos cronica. Baldomero confirma que Regina vive alli y se lo cuenta a su patron. Entonces Valerio la visita pero no la encuentra asi que se va hacia el resort. Rosarito le agradece a Natalia por haberla invitado a la discoteca y luego mira hacia una mesa y ve que se encuentra Gerardo, Vanessa y Luis Manuel. Por otro lado Gerardo tambien ve a Rosarito y se sorprende de lo bella que esta. Mas tarde Natalia da la bienvenida a Regina que va a cantar y en ese momento entra Adolfo con Pirana y la reconoce.

programme.title: El Talisman
programme.desc: Elvira acusa a Camila de estar destruyendo su matrimonio con Renato, ya que el le insinuo a Elvira que no tendria acceso a una cuenta bancaria, por miedo a que su hija la manipule para robarle su dinero. Elvira cree que Camila acabara con su matrimonio, pero Camila se decide aclarar la situacion con Renato. Luego se entera por Tracy que Renato era un farsante, tal como ella creia. - Mientras tanto, Renato espera cobrar el cheque de Elvira en el banco, pero alli le dicen que el cheque no puede cobrarse por haber expirado. Ahora Renato siente que ha perdido su posibilidad de hacerse rico, y ademas sigue casado con Elvira. - Lucrecia le sugiere a Pedro hacer un pacto de amor, y Pedro acepta a mala gana. Camila ve como ellos parecen amarse, y cree que Pedro solo jugo con ella todo el tiempo.

programme.title: Cosita Rica
programme.desc: Paula C. es la muchacha mas popular del barrio Republica. Posee un angel que la hace inolvidable y encantadora. Por eso, el dia que Diego Lujan, el joven empresario y futuro heredero de un imperio de cosmeticos, se cruzo con ella, se le marcaron sus ojos para siempre en la memoria. Diego estaba a una semana de casarse con la modelo mas hermosa de la ciudad: Vicky Cardenas. Ella era la imagen exclusiva de las empresas Avila y la afortunada prometida de un soltero impenitente y codiciado, como siempre se le habia conocido a Diego. Pero el destino jugo sus cartas. El encuentro entre Paula C. y Diego fue lo mas parecido a una tormenta, o lo que es lo mismo, a una gran historia de amor. Porque a Paula C. le paso exactamente lo mismo cuando vio a Diego: el estremecimiento de un huracan.

programme.title: Por Amarte Tanto
programme.desc: Laura es una bella joven heredera de una millonaria fortuna. Sin embargo, todo ese dinero no le ha causado mas que dolores de cabeza y al corazon, mientras espera encontrar algun dia el verdadero amor. Lamentablemente para Laura, el hombre que ahora intenta ganarse su corazon es una sanguijuela. Todo lo que busca es su dinero y la seguridad financiera que puede darle. Su sueno siempre ha sido encontrar a una rica y bella heredera y Laura es la chica que escoge como blanco. Al mismo tiempo, este hombre tiene un romance con la salvaje y peligrosa prima de Laura, por la que siente una ardiente pasion.

programme.title: Ines Duarte - Secretaria
programme.desc: Esta magistral historia narra los hechos que marcaron la vida de Ines Duarte, una joven secretaria a quien la sobreproteccion maternal convirtio en un ser reprimido, en una persona gris, en una desconocedora total de su potencial como mujer. Ines Duarte es una secretaria eficiente, muy util, muy fiel, muy trabajadora. Ella es la sombra de un gran magnate, Andres Martan. Ines lo resuelve todo, ella es casi necesaria para su jefe. El y su trabajo son la razon de su vida. Poco a poco, la pasion va haciendose mas presente en el corazon de Ines, colmandolo del mas fiel y secreto amor. Pero la vida de Andres va por otros caminos, para el, Ines es poco mas que un robot programado para servirle. Un matrimonio, hijos, viudez y mucha amargura van conformando el cuadro de la vida de Andres Martan, convirtiendolo en un hombre duro, encerrado en si mismo, en un despota. Pero los grandes cambios vendran, una nueva Ines irrumpira en la trama dando un vuelco total a los acontecimientos, creando multiples e inesperadas situaciones que sorprenderan y atraparan al televidente en las redes de esta formidable novela.

Pero los grandes cambios vendran, una nueva Ines irrumpira en la trama dando un vuelco total a los acontecimientos, creando multiples e inesperadas situaciones que sorprenderan y atraparan al televidente en las redes de esta formidable novela.

programme.title: La Mujer Perfecta
programme.desc: En este capitulo de esta apasionante historia de amores que se entrecruzan, luego de que Polanco le exige a Minerva que reincorpore a su puesto de trabajo a Micaela y pida disculpas delante de todo el personal, le pide a su chofer, Hinojosa que la lleve hasta su casa. Alli, Minerva e Hinojosa mantienen una conversacion en privado. Hinojosa le hace entender que ella es importante para el, y Minerva, que se siente mal por la actitud despectiva de Polanco; asi pues, ella se entrega a los brazos de Hinojosa. Por otro lado Nella consigue pasar la tarde con Saturno en su cama, mientras Estrella sigue sonando con la salida que hicieron juntos, el profesor Saturno y ella ¿Que pasara con esta relacion? ¿Saturno jugara a estar con Nella y con Estrella al mismo tiempo?

programme.title: Natalia del Mar
programme.desc: Patricia pide perdon, ella no queria que eso pasara y ahora todos corren peligro de muerte. Regina se siente ansiosa porque esta noche debuta como cantante en la discoteca del resort y le dice a su hermana que cuando cobre el primer sueldo la va a llevar a un medico para que se cure de su tos cronica. Baldomero confirma que Regina vive alli y se lo cuenta a su patron. Entonces Valerio la visita pero no la encuentra asi que se va hacia el resort. Rosarito le agradece a Natalia por haberla invitado a la discoteca y luego mira hacia una mesa y ve que se encuentra Gerardo, Vanessa y Luis Manuel. Por otro lado Gerardo tambien ve a Rosarito y se sorprende de lo bella que esta. Mas tarde Natalia da la bienvenida a Regina que va a cantar y en ese momento entra Adolfo con Pirana y la reconoce.

programme.title: El Talisman
programme.desc: Elvira acusa a Camila de estar destruyendo su matrimonio con Renato, ya que el le insinuo a Elvira que no tendria acceso a una cuenta bancaria, por miedo a que su hija la manipule para robarle su dinero. Elvira cree que Camila acabara con su matrimonio, pero Camila se decide aclarar la situacion con Renato. Luego se entera por Tracy que Renato era un farsante, tal como ella creia. - Mientras tanto, Renato espera cobrar el cheque de Elvira en el banco, pero alli le dicen que el cheque no puede cobrarse por haber expirado. Ahora Renato siente que ha perdido su posibilidad de hacerse rico, y ademas sigue casado con Elvira. - Lucrecia le sugiere a Pedro hacer un pacto de amor, y Pedro acepta a mala gana. Camila ve como ellos parecen amarse, y cree que Pedro solo jugo con ella todo el tiempo.

programme.title: Cosita Rica
programme.desc: Paula C. es la muchacha mas popular del barrio Republica. Posee un angel que la hace inolvidable y encantadora. Por eso, el dia que Diego Lujan, el joven empresario y futuro heredero de un imperio de cosmeticos, se cruzo con ella, se le marcaron sus ojos para siempre en la memoria. Diego estaba a una semana de casarse con la modelo mas hermosa de la ciudad: Vicky Cardenas. Ella era la imagen exclusiva de las empresas Avila y la afortunada prometida de un soltero impenitente y codiciado, como siempre se le habia conocido a Diego. Pero el destino jugo sus cartas. El encuentro entre Paula C. y Diego fue lo mas parecido a una tormenta, o lo que es lo mismo, a una gran historia de amor. Porque a Paula C. le paso exactamente lo mismo cuando vio a Diego: el estremecimiento de un huracan.

programme.title: Por Amarte Tanto
programme.desc: Laura es una bella joven heredera de una millonaria fortuna. Sin embargo, todo ese dinero no le ha causado mas que dolores de cabeza y al corazon, mientras espera encontrar algun dia el verdadero amor. Lamentablemente para Laura, el hombre que ahora intenta ganarse su corazon es una sanguijuela. Todo lo que busca es su dinero y la seguridad financiera que puede darle. Su sueno siempre ha sido encontrar a una rica y bella heredera y Laura es la chica que escoge como blanco. Al mismo tiempo, este hombre tiene un romance con la salvaje y peligrosa prima de Laura, por la que siente una ardiente pasion.

programme.title: Ines Duarte - Secretaria
programme.desc: Esta magistral historia narra los hechos que marcaron la vida de Ines Duarte, una joven secretaria a quien la sobreproteccion maternal convirtio en un ser reprimido, en una persona gris, en una desconocedora total de su potencial como mujer. Ines Duarte es una secretaria eficiente, muy util, muy fiel, muy trabajadora. Ella es la sombra de un gran magnate, Andres Martan. Ines lo resuelve todo, ella es casi necesaria para su jefe. El y su trabajo son la razon de su vida. Poco a poco, la pasion va haciendose mas presente en el corazon de Ines, colmandolo del mas fiel y secreto amor. Pero la vida de Andres va por otros caminos, para el, Ines es poco mas que un robot programado para servirle. Un matrimonio, hijos, viudez y mucha amargura van conformando el cuadro de la vida de Andres Martan, convirtiendolo en un hombre duro, encerrado en si mismo, en un despota. programme.title: La Mujer Perfecta

Lucia se siente muy angustiada y piensa en no seguir adelante con esa relacion. Minerva e Hinojosa tienen un encuentro intimo en la casa de ella, a pesar de que son conscientes de que hay camaras de Polanco por todas partes. Bambi lleva a Chantal a la mansion de Polanco para que pase la noche junto a el, pero Chantal se siente incomoda y no entiende la propuesta que le hizo Bambi, la cual es que ella debe acostarse con Polanco a cambio de dinero.

programme.title: AmeriCarna
programme.desc: In this episode, Ray celebrates the 50th birthday of the Ford Mustang through the lens of three distinct Mustang owners, who each hold a slice of the car’s incredible history. In 1964, Chicago schoolteacher Gail Wise unknowingly purchased the first ever Mustang 3 days before the car became available to the general public. Her husband reveals the incredible restoration that brought the earliest Mustang ever sold back to its 60’s glory. (Ford Motor Company knows she has the car and has verified it was sold before it was legal to sell.) John Grafelman is a farmer in Illinois and life-long Ford lover. A few years ago he found an old car hidden in a barn. It took some time, but he eventually convinced his friend to sell it to him. After some detective work, he discovers he purchased 1968 Ford Design Chief Larry Shinoda’s personal car that he tinkered with to invent the BOSS 302.Lastly, Ray travels to Dayton Ohio to interview Gale Holderman, the Ford stylist who won the company’s contest to draw and design the Mustang.

programme.title: AmeriCarna
programme.desc: Post-World War II, a large generation of American soldiers was looking for cars that mirrored the incredible sports cars they saw overseas in Europe. After searching for an affordable way to recreate these cars, one manufacturer responded with a durable, cost effective option: a line of fiberglass sports cars. Very few of these cars still exist but there are collectors who are constantly looking to save parts and pieces of these virtually unknown vehicles. We learn about these rare cars from Geoff Hacker and his team at Forgotten Fiberglass, and take a visit to the Smithsonian Museum, which houses a fiberglass car of its own. This episode presents a unique look at how the narrative of American wartime experiences often shaped the nation’s automotive demands.

programme.title: AmeriCarna
programme.desc: Ray explores buying a unique, hand built car the Schultz family has kept in their New Jersey home for years. The car was originally called the Schultz El Fierro but it’s officially titled in New Jersey as a “Schultz Special” from 1958. It was used to drag race and held numerous racing records, but most important to the family was that it was driven by the legendary Carroll Shelby. With a frame and style much similar to the Shelby Roadster, the Schultz family wonders if it inspired one of the most well known automobiles in America. In another epic New Jersey story, Ray finds Mario Andretti’s 1965 IndyCar. The catch: it’s completely in pieces hidden away in a garage. The iconic driver talks about his days on the track with that car and Ray attempts to negotiate a deal to buy the parts.

programme.title: AmeriCarna
programme.desc: How do you cast a car in a movie? What are the secrets to the build? Hollywood car designers give Ray the ultimate tour of some memorable movie cars, including a look at the recently found “Hells Chariot”, the last surviving car from Grease. We also hear the backstory to “Bumble Bee” from Transformers, take a look at the making of the tanks for Hunger Games and stumble upon the iconic 1958 Chevy Impala from American Graffiti.

programme.title: AmeriCarna
programme.desc: While visiting the estate of automotive genius and land speed record holder Willie Glass, Ray uncovers a set of extremely rare Ardun cylinder heads, which is a hot rodders dream discovery. He also visits the infamous H & H Flatheads outside of Los Angeles and discovers a surprise connection to the Earnhardt family.

programme.title: AmeriCarna
programme.desc: A massive sinkhole opened underneath the National Corvette Museum in Kentucky. Eight amazing cars were swallowed up, including the 1,000,000th Corvette. AmeriCarna was given exclusive access to document the removal of the cars from the sinkhole and the painstaking restoration of the 1,000,000th Corvette.

programme.desc: Amelia Island's own Caffeine & Octane car show,: Featuring $2,000 Wrek Racing Truck, David Patterson's favorite C&O cars, a plastic Citroen Mehari, and much more.

programme.title: Caffeine & Octane
programme.desc: The Concours d'Elegance from Amelia Island: Featuring bomb-proof Conquest Knight XV, '69 Camaro Hagerty Fixer-Upper, and car-enthusiast John Oates.

programme.title: Caffeine & Octane
programme.sub-title: Delta Wing Racer with a Vengeance
programme.desc: State-of-the-art engineering and passion projects take center stage on this edition of Caffeine & Octane. The revolutionary Delta Wing Racer turns on hot lap after hot lap at Road Atlanta, and driver Katherine Legge offers insight on how “less is more” when it comes to power to weight ratios; the dark world of a graffiti artist paints a picture of a car called Vengeance while the hosts share the eclectic hybrids of machines that make it to Caffeine and Octane with Vengance’s creator Totem.

programme.title: Caffeine & Octane
programme.desc: The word is out that Caffeine & Octane is the ultimate scene and the place to be seen. Even after 12 hours of racing at the Petit Le Mans endurance race, Henry Ford III, the great grandson of Henry Ford the industrial magnate and current member of Ford’s Board of Directors, showed up to take in the sights, address the crowds, and sign a one of a kind Ford Shelby GT350R. The GT350R will hit the road with Operation Hope to encourage young people to study math and science through motorsports; Covert car counterfeiter, Chuck Beck looks for Ford’s approval on his own version of a muscled up Festiva. YouTuber ‘That Dude in Blue’ David Patterson joins Skip and Bryan to get a special look at the motor-based philanthropic outreach and amazing cars that come with it done by John Hope Bryant, friend of Caffeine and Octane.

programme.title: Caffeine & Octane
programme.desc: Rickey and Bryan race outside of their comfort zones, each competing to find the raddest car collection. Rickey hangs out with classic racer, Ron Green, who shows him the ropes in the ultra light '83 Ralt RT5. Bryan visits a collection of 120 racing motorcycle owned by mechanic and racer Mike McConville. Mike takes Bryan motorcross racing in his backyard after showing off his high horsepowered car collection. Caffeine and Octane alongside Ron Green visit Atlanta's first Concours d'elegance to look at classic cars that have been perfectly maintained for decades.

programme.title: Caffeine & Octane
programme.sub-title: The Wrap on the Most Beautiful Cars
programme.desc: Wayne Phears’ Jaguar E-Type was nothing more than a diamond in the rough before the mineral rights attorney took on the basket case. Caffeine & Octane brings viewers the story of how Phears’, through relentless research and determination, restored and reunited the #10 Jag that Enzo Ferrari called “the most beautiful car ever made”; Atlanta Wraps shows how wrapping Corvettes and Lamborghinis can color a car fast. Caffeine and Exotics is featured again to show off the coolest wraps Atlanta can supply.

programme.title: Caffeine & Octane
programme.desc: Twenty-five years of hand building record-setting race cars is no easy task. But don’t tell that to Don Panoz who takes on Porsches and Ferraris with his laid back personality and a full-production facility that makes improvised versions of Americas V-8’s; Caffeine & Octane gets an exclusive look at an elusive man’s life long pursuit of everything Chevrolet.

programme.title: Caffeine & Octane
programme.desc: Caffeine & Octane goes old school with Psycho Deville singer and pin striper Walt Richards. Richards has less than a week to hand paint his signature flames on a way cool ’50 Mercury. An introduction to Retrofit Lighting’s trickle down technology - from cars to motorcycles - that will revolutionize how bikes will see and be seen.

programme.title: Caffeine & Octane
programme.sub-title: Beetles, Bugs, and Buses, Oh My!
programme.desc: Caffeine & Octane is known for having something for everyone. That reputation is tested when over 100 VW’s, on the lunatic fringe of automotive, rattled into an event. The annual VW Invasion has swarmed C&O, bringing with it Bugs, Beetles, Buses and more by a very dedicated VW fan base.

programme.title: Caffeine & Octane
programme.desc: Rapper, radio, and ATL TV personality Darian “Big Tigger” Morgan invites Caffeine & Octane into his home. Cameras look past his collection of 500 Michael Jordan shoes to focus their lenses on a one-off motorcycle the 6–time NBA Champion gave to Tigger as a gift; A second to none, muscle car collection by one of the founders of Monster Energy gets toured by one of our hosts.

programme.title: Caffeine & Octane
programme.desc: Vintage Testarossas and Quatra Valve Ferraris don’t just show up on a dealer’s floor, they’re hunted! Adam Merlin, exotic car expert, has spent a lifetime searching for the cars that defined his youth, but nothing is assumed or given in his high stakes game of Risk; A muscle car fiend shows off his private collection to host Skip Smith.

programme.title: Caffeine & Octane
programme.desc: The word is out that Caffeine & Octane is the major league of North American car shows. Former Atlanta Brave, World Series star, and 10-Time Gold Glove winner Andruw Jones acknowledged the stardom and showed up to show off his 6 wheeled Super Jeep. The state of the art creation took years in planning and execution, but Jones chooses one great event for its debut.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: This is the moment you’ve been waiting for! Master car builder, Stacey David, shows off the truck that’s had the nation talking for ten years! Take a look back at the kid with the dream. Follow the design and fabrication. See what happens when the military tribute vehicle rolls out and conquers the road! This episode is gonna be epic. It’s been a long road, but anything worth doing well is worth the wait. This week, the wait is over. Sergeant Rock Lives!

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.sub-title: On the Road & Unicure Spray Booths
programme.desc: Things are rockin’ and rollin’ in and out of the GearZ garage. Stacey hits the road to find a project build that will get gear heads buzzing. He ends up with an ’81 Camaro and some awesome stories from the seller. If you’re talking project vehicles, you’ve got to talk paint! And Stacey does just that with folks from Unicure, who specialize in paint booths and helping you get set up for that all important paint job. The V-8 Interceptor is back from a trip to Stainless works, where a custom exhaust system was made for the big Boss Nine engine. Things are about to get loud, this week on GearZ.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.sub-title: The Return of Heavy Metal & Snowcat
programme.desc: Stacey and the GearZ crew roll in an old favorite: Heavy Metal. The coolest hotrod tow truck is back in the garage and ready for a facelift. Our good friends at the Hot Rod Institute drop by and talk shop with Stacey about his plans for the paint and fab work needed to get this bad boy looking good and back on the road. Fresh from the sandblaster, the snowcat reveals the scars that were under the skin. And with the drive train out, Stacey walks through the importance of replacing gaskets, seals and checking for wear and tear before stuffing that engine, transmission and skid steer rear end back into the cat. There’s a whole lot going on this week on GearZ.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: Every gear head has a secret: they all want to drive like McQueen in Bullitt, or Vin Diesel in The Fast And The Furious. But when the heat gets turned up, even some really good drivers can’t keep up. That’s when you bring in the Stunt Double! This week Stacey sits down with legendary Hollywood stunt man Ian Quinn to talk crashing cars and keeping actors out of harms way. There’s also a new project in the garage: The Stunt Double, a build inspired by the 80’s tv show The Fall Guy, and sure to get all four wheels off the ground before Stacey’s done with it. Sparks are going to fly and you know we’re gonna have a good time this week on GearZ.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: Seems like you can’t go more than a block these days without running into someone whose had some work done on their face. Well, here at the GearZ garage, Stacey believes in facelifts too. Just to prove it, he’s taken on a 1981 Camaro and sharpened his scalpel to perform an automotive nose job. Just wait till you see him whack of the old rubber nose and replace it with a 71’ rally sport front end! Now that’s what we call a facelift. Plenty of people said it couldn’t be done, but that’s just the kind of challenge Stacey is up for. Plenty of sparks are gonna fly, this week on GearZ.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: They say that true change comes from within… Well, this week Stacey turns his attention to the interior of the Stunt Double. The old, crusty junk hits the floor and our Fall Guy inspired build gets a new look: from painting trim and door panels, to a new bench seat. Man o’ man, this truck is starting to look completely different. A shower of sparks lights up the garage as Stacey demonstrates how to make a bracket that mounts our new bench seat to the truck while using the stock seat adjustment. It’s a tour de force of aftermarket parts and salvaging what we’ve got, this week on GearZ!

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: When you’re putting together a project that’s inspired by a high-flying stunt truck, you know you’ve got to add some lift, and our Stunt Double gets the goods this week. The front and rear suspension get treated to a 6” lift to get that rig up in the air. But a good lift won’t do any good if the steering and frame can’t hold up, so Stacey shows you how Offroad Design has fixed some serious issues that many late model four-wheel drives encounter. Bed need to come off your truck, but the carriage bolts are rusted and spinning? Stacey’s got a fix for that too. There’s a lot going on, and we’ve got you covered, this week on GearZ.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: Everyone needs a little boost here and there. For some people, coffee does the trick. But here in the GearZ Garage we take our boost seriously. And we like ours packing 160 HP. Hang on to your seat as Stacey adds a bolt on Supercharger to a Ram 1500 breathes a little excitement into a daily driver. And speaking of things going on in the garage, you’ll definitely want to stick around as Stacey talks shop with the guys at Rebuilding Generations. Learn all about how this mentoring program is teaching the next generation about working on cars and sharing plenty of life lessons. We’ve got a lot going on this week on GearZ.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: We’re running full steam ahead as the Stunt Double rolls back into the shop this week! First, Stacey reveals the wheels and tires that are going to accentuate that 6” lift, then He dives headlong into the drivetrain of this beast and comes up with a hot crate engine and a high-performance transmission to get the Stunt Double ready for the road. But that’s not all…. We also take some time out for a visit with the guys from American Powertrain and so much more. Check out the sparks flying in the garage this week on GearZ.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: It’s business as usual in the garage this week. We’re back at work on the Catalog Camaro and really diggin’ into the front end. You know what they say, “out with the old and in with the new,” and that’s exactly what Stacey’s doing. The old sub frame, drivetrain, and suspension are hitting the garage floor in favor of a much-needed updated suspension system that’ll keep this awesome Camaro hugging the road at high speeds—From the wheels to the sub frame, Stacey’s replacing it all. And he’s not going to break the bank while doing it, either. Follow the GearZ crew as they hit the road and visit Cornwell Tools to see their latest and greatest tool box being manufactured. From powder coat to knuckle bustin’ bolts, we’ve got you covered this week on GearZ.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: We head out of the garage to visit one of the premiere supercharger manufacturers in the world… ATI Pro Charger. Follow along for the ride as Stacey walks through the entire process of how they have raised the bar on how a supercharger is built and what it does. From bulk metal to dyno runs, we’ve got it covered. Back in the garage, a young Gearhead drops by to learn how to install an air intake and cowl induction hood on his pick-up. After the wrench turning is done, he and Stacey have enough time to hit a few licks on their guitars. From massive horsepower increases with state-of-the-art tools and machinery, to simple intake and hood installs,….. it’s all here, this week on GearZ.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: Stacey is in full hot rod mode as he unveils a wicked LS engine and Tremec 6spd tranny and stuffs it into the Catalog Camaro. If 600hp and a 6spd in a Camaro doesn’t get you going, the update on the Stunt Double will! It’s old school cool as Stacey shows off the stainless light bar, side steps and cutout flairs to give the truck that “Fall Guy” vibe. After that we introduce you to the amazing world of scale R/C that is sure to have you re-thinking what you want for Christmas! Finally we roll in some updates on the Cheetah and the Junkyard Jag too. If you’re a gearhead, you’re gonna find a whole lot to love about this show!......and that’s GEARZ!!!

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: Season 12 opens with bang as Stacey starts the final assembly process on the V8 Interceptor. If you’ve ever wondered how to lay out an aftermarket A/C system, wiring harness, and steering column on your project… and make them all work together, you have to see this show! After that, NHRA legend and Hall-of-Famer, Doug Herbert drops by the GearZ garage to share the shocking story that inspired him to start the B.R.A.K.E.S. driving program. Hold on tight, because this ain't your typical high school driver's Ed. Program! If you want cool tech and awesome stories… you’re gonna find that on GEARZ!

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: It’s all about fabrication and thinking outside the box, or to be more specific... outside the bed! Sure, sure, there are plenty of custom pick-up truck beds you can buy but Stacey shows you what is involved in MAKING a custom bed to fit any vehicle, even something as crazy as a Thiokol Imp snowcat! That's right… our little snowcat is back from the sand blaster and ready for a cool bed to match the cab. Stacey goes in-depth about sizing up the project, picking the right parts, and most importantly: how to cut, weld, grind and finish sheet metal to get a bed that will fit your unique vehicle like a glove. So grab a welder… it’s time to make your bed!... only on GearZ.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: Stacey takes a trip to Fort Carson, Colorado to visit the Army auto skills program during their world conference. Not only does Stacey get to meet a General, but he also meets a young Sergeant who is in the middle of a frame-off square body restoration. After a thorough walk around, Stacey decides to get LMC involved in helping out with this build. Parts for the bed of his truck can’t match the gratitude we share for our active military and all those who have served, but it’s a start. And we can’t wait to see the project when it’s finished. And speaking of new beds, with the custom bed on the Snow Cat, it’s time to address the tracks, and Right Track Systems has us covered. That little cat is going to tear it up when all is said and done! It’s going to be a lot of fun, this week on GearZ.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: It’s all about Cougars! No, not that kind of Cougar... the kind with 4 wheels and a legendary pedigree! After a short history lesson about how these cars came into existence and why they were so cool, Stacey rolls the V8 Interceptor back into the shop and digs into the final assembly of this wild ’67 Mercury Cougar. This week’s episode focuses on planning out your final assembly, and taking care of all the little details, before you put the big things in like engine and transmission. Whether it’s planning out your brake system, battery location, or running fuel lines, Stacey shows how a little extra time in the planning department will make all the difference in your build.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: Stacey takes us through the history of the legendary SR-71 Blackbird. If you’re not familiar with this bird, it could fly mach 3.2, cruise at 80,000 feet and kept our country safe through its many reconnaissance missions. Never shot down, and never outrun, it was the hot rod of the sky! Stacey gets to sit down with pilot Lt. Col. Ed Yeilding and talk about his record setting transcontinental flight—Coast to Coast in 67 minutes and 54 seconds! The iconic Blackbird was such an inspiration that you know Stacey had to make a vehicle inspired by and paying tribute to it, so get ready to meet the SR-71 Rapid Tool Express!!!

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.sub-title: Catalog Camaro Butt Lift and Tummy Tuck
programme.desc: The Catalog Camaro is back in the garage and ready to go under the knife as Stacey shows how to do a butt lift and tummy tuck on a 2nd generation Camaro. What does that mean? Well, last season Stacey performed a nose job on this old ’81 Camaro to show how easy it is to get rid of the 80’s plastic front bumpers and put on the classic early 70’s split-bumper, rally sport front sheetmetal. This week he continues the makeover by losing the plastic rear bumper and wrap-around taillights and grafting in the early 70’s quarter panels, round taillights and chrome bumper. It’s more in depth than the front and definitely requires some skilled metal surgery, but Stacey shows you all the tricks on how to do it properly. So, sit back and enjoy the ride as Stacey details how to measure, cut, and weld your way to a much younger looking Camaro.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: Stacey rolls in a Big Bad Buick Riviera and shows you what is possible with the right vehicle and some bolt on parts. This 1972 Riviera is a great entry-level project that won’t break the bank, and has the potential to serve some serious humble-pie to any unsuspecting hot shot that may want to mix it up at the stoplight. As it sits, the big 455 under the hood is a force to be reckoned with, but Stacey shows what a weekend in the garage and a top end rebuild can do for a car like this! Get ready to get your hands dirty and bust a few knuckles as Stacey pulls the old heads, intake, cam, and ignition off and replaces them with performance parts from companies like TA Performance, Edelbrock, and MSD. It’s a lesson in Buick and bolt-on horsepower, and you’re only gonna find it on GearZ.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: The GearZ crew hits the road this week and travels to the Charlotte Speed Shop to see how paint prep is going on Stacey’s Cheetah Evolution Car. With the hood and side vents glassed in and smoothed out, the first coat of primer gets sprayed and this awesome cat takes one big step closer to coming home! Stacey also stops by to visit with a fellow boat tail Riviera owner and trade tips on beefing up these classic beauties. It turns out that this guy and Stacey had both been watching this same car when it came up for sale! Come hang out with us as we visit some great folks this week on GearZ.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: Stacey gets down to business on the Big Bad Buick. With the top end engine rebuilt, the exterior and interior of the car need some serious updating. You don’t have to spend a ton of cash on simple modifications. Stacey shows what’s behind making a good clean line with your bumpers and how a simple front and rear bumper tuck can drastically change the appearance. Replacing the grille and scraping off that old vinyl top are also sure-fire ways to add attitude to this big ol’ boat tail. That old carpet has got to go! Follow along as Stacey shows the ins and outs and some tips and tricks to keep your exterior and interior redo from breaking the bank.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: Not everyone out there is wrenching on an a classic. In fact, we get tons of emails from viewers who want to upgrade brand-new vehicles but aren’t sure how to get started. Well, Stacey has the answer—and it comes with a little help from our friend and NASCAR legend Jimmie Johnson and a stunning 2018 Camaro SS. Come hang out in the garage as Stacey walks you through the top seven modifications that you can make to a car that you just drove off the lot! Everything from paint upgrades to wheels, Stacey’s got a list. Let’s get started!

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: Stacey’s hard at work on a 2018 Camaro SS. This build is super-cool, not only because he’s running down a list of the top seven mods you can make on a brand-new car, but also because seven-time NASCAR champion, Jimmie Johnson is involved with the project. We’ve covered paint mods, body mods, and interior mods. Now it’s time to go under the hood and under the car and talk powers gains and handling upgrades!

Judwaa
programme.desc: Judwaa is a story about twins Raja and Prem Malhotra who separate at birth. Years later, they reunite to defeat Ratanlal, a local gangster, who wants to destroy the Malhotra family.

programme.title: Bhagam Bhag
programme.desc: Bunty and Babla are two wannabe actors and want to play the lead in their theatre’s play. Soon, their inappropriate behaviour causes the female lead to quit and they get tasked to finding another which hilariously lands them in a convoluted trouble.

programme.title: Heyy Babyy
programme.desc: Aarush, Al and Tanmay, three womanisers get the shock of their life when they find a baby girl at their doorstep claiming to be the daughter of one of them. As they try to find her mother, they discover an unexplored side of their own personality.

programme.title: Aavishkar
programme.desc: Amar and Mansi live a rather peaceful and happy married life, that is, until Amar's job in an advertising agency requires him to work closely with beautiful models, which leads to some serious trouble in paradise.

programme.title: Ustadi Ustad Se
programme.desc: After their region is hit by floods, young Seema (Ranjeeta Kaur) is separated from her childhood friend, Rajesh (Mithun Chakraborty) and her rowdy admirer Sanjay (Vinod Mehra). Years later, she is reunited with Rajesh and they decide to get married. But on the wedding day, a woman shows up with a child and claims to be his wife.

programme.title: Zed Plus
programme.desc: A political satire set in a small town in Rajasthan where the local government is on the verge of collapsing due to factors such as corruption and mismanagement.

programme.title: Jab We Met
programme.desc: The life of a suicidal industrialist takes a sharp turn when he meets a spirited chatterbox on a train journey in this breezy Bollywood romantic comedy.

programme.title: Dil Ka Rishta
programme.desc: Jai unintentionally kills the husband of a woman that he loves. When she gets diagnosed with amnesia, Jai comforts her and she falls in love with him. Now, guilt-ridden Jai is left in a dilemma whether to confess his guilt or reciprocate her love.

programme.title: GLORY Kickboxing
programme.desc: The event will be headlined by an exhilarating heavyweight matchup between No. 1 ranked contender Antonio Plazibat and No. 10 ranked contender Raul Catinas. Co-headlining the event is a Welterweight Title Bout between Alim Nabiyev and Endy Semeleer. Also featured on the card, MMA veteran Joilton Lutterbach will make his GLORY debut against fellow debutant Mark Trijsburg in a welterweight bout. Top-five lightweight contender Itay Gershon will make his return to the GLORY ring against promotional newcomer Cihad Akipa. The card will also mark the return of perennial heavyweight contender Jahfarr Wilnis, who will be making his first appearance on the GLORY stage since 2019. He will meet promotional newcomer Michal Blawdziewicz.

programme.title: GLORY Kickboxing
programme.desc: GLORY 85 will feature the four-man heavyweight tournament featuring two-time tournament finalist Jahfarr Wilnis (33-13-1, 8 KO), Heavyweight newcomer Murat Aygun (33-3-0), Nigerian giant Tariq ‘Cookie’ Osaro (22-2-1), and ‘The Iron Bull’ Enver Sljivar (40-6, 23 KO). A kickboxing legend will also make his return on April 29 as former two-time GLORY champion Murthel Groenhart (69-25-3, 40 KO) challenges current welterweight champion Endy Semeleer (33-1, 17 KO) for the title.

programme.title: GLORY Kickboxing
programme.desc: In the main event, featherweight champ Petch (168-39-3, 27 KO) looks to defend his crown for the sixth time when he welcomes the challenge of local hero Ahmad Chikh Mousa (58-8-1, 28 KO). The co-main event will see a crucial fight between Romania’s Benjamin Adegbuyi (35-8, 20 KO) and Sofian Laïdouni (35-2-1, 17 KO) of France that will decide who will qualify for the GLORY Heavyweight Grand Prix in December.

programme.title: GLORY Kickboxing
programme.desc: The interim-GLORY Heavyweight Title will be up for grabs as top ranked heavyweight contender Antonio Plazibat (22-4, 16 KO) collides with the number two ranked Tariq ‘Cookie’ Osaro (24-2-1, 12 KO) in the main event. These teammates will have to put their friendship aside for one night and go head-to-head for GLORY gold. Also on the card are title fights in the Middleweight, Welterweight and Light Heavyweight divisions.

programme.title: GLORY Kickboxing

programme.title: Chain Letter
programme.desc: Six friends receive a mysterious chain letter via text and email from a maniac who hunts down those who delete the message. Who knew they should take the threats in the chain letter seriously or that their favorite technologies could help track and kill them?

programme.title: Charade
programme.desc: Romance and suspense ensue in Paris as a woman is pursued by several men who want a fortune her murdered husband had stolen. Who can she trust?

programme.title: Cherzoso The Silent Film
programme.desc: Cherzoso is a short silent film about family, life choices and consequences.

programme.title: Circle
programme.desc: In this exciting thriller the FBI teams up with U.S. marshals in pursuit of an escaped sociopath, James Bennett, after he commits a series of meticulously planned murders. To further complicate matters, they learn Bennet is headed to his childhood home where a group of graduate students are studying his surroundings in order to write their thesis

programme.title: Civilian
programme.desc: In an operation during his military duty, Emrah (21) has killed a guerilla and found a notebook with a letter in it. Back to his home, he starts a search to find the recipient of the letter, while losing himself in his inner world.

programme.title: Claudiu And The Fish
programme.desc: Claudiu, 28 year old, works at the fresh fish department of a big supermarket, pitying the live carps crammed into a small, overpacked aquarium. After seeing one of these fish coughing like a human being, Claudiu, seriously troubled by the episode, asks his boss if he can bring a bigger aquarium, where the carps can feel more comfortable. Following a humiliating refusal from the boss, Claudiu decides to take revenge by making a bomb threat call and causing the evacuation of the entire store. But his satisfaction doesn’t last for too long: Claudiu learns that his prank call just sentenced to death all the living fish and thus he’s forced to go back inside the empty store and rescue them.

programme.title: CONVENTO
programme.desc: A Dutch family left Holland to transform a 400 year old monastery into a home, artist's workshop, and nature preserve. Filmed entirely in remote village in Portugal, Convento bends the rigid structure of documentary filmmaking, blurring the lines of information and surrealism Featuring the renowned kinetic artist Christiaan Zwanikken and his family.

programme.title: Crossroads
programme.desc: Valery Liashkevich is now considered an important Belarus artist - but just one year ago, he was living in the railway station and for over twenty years has painted pictures in the streets of the town of Gomel. For the natives he is no more than a local attraction, but the filmmakers set out to show that this eccentric artist and philosopher has many impor-tant truths to tell us about the meaning of life, that his work and attitude to the world make deep sense.

programme.title: Cyrano de Bergerac
programme.desc: The charismatic swordsman-poet helps another woo the woman he loves in this straightforward version of the play.

programme.title: Dark Moon Rising
programme.desc: Small-town girl meets mysterious drifter boy, they fall in love. Only in this case, the boy brings with him a family curse and unimaginable horror that rains hell upon the small town.

programme.title: Day Zero

programme.desc: El malvado hechicero Gargamel acude una vez mas a Esmeralda, la adivinadora, la cual se las ingenia para hacerse con el dinero de Gargamel. Cuando es el turno de los Pitufos, les hace creer que existe un arbol de la suerte...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Cuando el Pitufo Filosofo pierde sus gafas deja caer las cosas, tropieza con los objetos, y se convierte en tan patoso como el Pitufo Tontin, que ahora tiene que leer a Filosofo y ayudarle a manejarse. Esta experiencia hace que Filosofo se sienta culpable por la forma en la que siempre se ha burlado de Tontin. Una vez que recibe un nuevo par de gafas, le trata con mas respeto.

programme.title: La Absopitufiasombrosa Maquina
programme.desc: Pitufo Genio inventa una maquina que hara que los Pitufos controlen el clima a su voluntad.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Para demostrar lo valido que es su «Gran libro de supervivencia en la naturaleza», Pitufo Filosofo se lleva a los Pitufitos al pantano. Alli, gracias a su experto consejo, el pequeno grupo se extravia, queda atrapado en arenas movedizas y es capturado por el Rey Verrugoso. Afortunadamente, el Rey Verrugoso esta con ganas de jugar y decide hacer una caza del Pitufo. Desafortunadamente, Pitufo Filosofo cree que es un lider por naturaleza...

programme.title: A Todas Las Criaturas Grandes Y Pequenas
programme.desc: Pitufo Natural esta convencido de que puede ayudar a todas las criaturas con sus dones curativos, incluso al malvado Azrael, cuya pata queda atrapada en una trampa. El gato se cura y, a pesar de que tiene la tentacion de quedarse con los Pitufos, regresa con Gargamel, pero conduce a su dueno hacia un lugar alejado de la Aldea Pitufa.

programme.title: ¿Como Hacer Un Arcoiris?
programme.desc: La madre naturaleza esta demasiado ocupada para evocar un Arcoiris para el Festival de los Pitufos, asi que Papa Pitufo pide prestado su libro de cocina para realizar la mezcla el mismo.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Papa Pitufo organiza un grupo para navegar a una lejana isla ya que Gargamel ha cortado todos los arboles menos uno para atrapar a los pitufos. Gargamel les sigue pero la Bruja de la isla acaba enviando sus gaviotas tras el.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Es cierto: lo bueno en exceso puede ser malo. Cuando se produce un accidente que afecta a la formula magica de Papa Pitufo y este acaba duplicado, los Pitufos se muestran encantados: dos Papas Pitufo pueden dar el doble de buenos consejos y el doble de amor que uno solo. Sin embargo, despues de un tiempo, las cosas se complican en exceso en la aldea. ¡Sobre todo cuando otro accidente hace que Gargamel tambien se duplique!

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Cada vez que Pitufo Perezoso se queda dormido, tiene la misma pesadilla una y otra vez: se encuentra en poder de Morfeo, un malvado hechicero que quiere capturar a tantas almas dormidas como sea posible. Uno tras otro, todos los Pitufos van cayendo en las garras de Morfeo. ¿Todos? Quiza no, si Papa Pitufo puede evitarlo. Para ello, Papa Pitufo acude al Arenero en busca de ayuda...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: La malvada bruja se transforma en Pitufo para vengarse de ellos por destruir su amuleto magico.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Las preocupaciones de Papa Pitufo hacen que le salgan verrugas. La unica forma de librarle de esta enfermedad causada por la indecision es que frote el cuerno de uno de los Verrugosos, los desalinados, viscosos, estupidos y brutales enemigos de las haditas del Bosque de los Sauces...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: En su busqueda de algo novedoso, Pitufo Vanidoso se pone un sombrero magico creado por Gargamel que le deja la cara hecha un adefesio. Mediante una argucia, Papa Pitufo consigue robarle el antidoto al malvado mago, logrando asi que Pitufo Vanidoso recupere su belleza.

programme.title: Hay Que Atrapar Al Ladron
programme.desc: Los Pitufos y Omnibus se hacen amigos de un desdichado joven cuyo maestro le obliga a robar. Pronto, el malvado ladron es entregado al magistrado y el joven esta encantado de irse a vivir con Omnibus.

programme.title: ¡alarma, Pitufos!
programme.desc: Los Pitufitos se sienten poco queridos y deciden huir. Se llevan consigo objetos que les recuerden su hogar, lo que hace que los Pitufos crean que hay un ladron entre ellos. Pitufo Filosofo intenta atrapar al ladron instalando pitufialarmas. Las alarmas provocan un estruendo que atrae a los Pitufitos de vuelta a casa, donde Papa Pitufo les convence de que los quieren.

programme.title: El Dia Libre De Papa Pitufo
programme.desc: Los Pitufos deciden que Papa Pitufo necesita un descanso, por lo que acuerdan resolver sus problemas sin su ayuda. Papa Pitufo se siente inutil, pero Omnibus, su sabio amigo, le muestra que los Pitufos no podrian arreglarselas sin el. Papa Pitufo regresa justo a tiempo para arreglar una presa que tiene fugas, y se siente util de nuevo.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Pitufo Grunon aprende que las emociones pueden ser fantasticas, sobre todo despues de que la malvada Clorhidris cree un corazon de hielo para despojar a todos de la bondad y el amor.

programme.title: Ya No Tengo Miedo
programme.desc: Una vez mas, el infalible plan de Gargamel para atrapar a los Pitufos ha fracasado. Los Pitufos aprovechan para gastarle una broma: disfrazados de pequenos angeles azules, le ensenaran a enmendar su conducta...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.sub-title: Pitufo Marco Y Los Piratas Pimienta
programme.desc: Los Pitufos navegan para salvar a Marco, que ha sido capturado por el Capitan Pedro Pimienta. Marina y un delfin acaban liberando a Marco.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Los Pitufos se preparan para recuperar una concha marina que necesitan para liberar a un ermitano de las garras de la Bruja del Mar, la cual la maldijo con un aspecto horrible y un lenguaje dificil de entender. Los Pitufos consiguen recuperar la concha a tiempo para romper el maleficio y devolver al ermitano a su verdadero ser.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Otra estupenda produccion del teatro de los Pitufos basada en los personajes de Alejandro Dumas. Incluye algunas lineas de Romeo y Julieta. Una obra maestra de la escena.

programme.title: El Pitufo Enmascarado
programme.desc: Una noche de Luna Azulada, tal y como la leyenda decia, un bebe pitufo aparece en el pueblo, y todos acaban agarrandole carino. Pero todo ha sido un malentendido y la ciguena vuelve por el bebe. Pintor y Grunon se han encarinado tanto con el bebe que les regresan al bebe.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: En su plan por librarse de los Pitufos, Gargamel le lanza un hechizo a Giganton y se disfraza de Pitufo. Creyendo que es un Pitufo, Giganton esta a punto de destrozar por completo la Aldea Pitufa hasta que Papa Pitufo acude con una cura.

programme.title: Las Crisis Del Fango
programme.desc: El Rey Verrugoso entra en panico porque la cosecha de fango esta siendo un fracaso. Decide capturar a Pitufo Labrador, el mayor experto en agricultura del mundo, para resolver su problema. Pitufo Labrador instala un sistema de riego y salva la cosecha. Despues, escapa en una burbuja y regresa con los demas Pitufos.

programme.title: El Bebe Pitufo
programme.desc: Gargamel se transforma en un Bebe Pitufo, para ser adoptado por los Pitufos. Causa un completo caos en la Aldea de los Pitufos cuando intenta hacerlos volar por los aires con una bomba. Papa Pitufo descubre su malvado plan y utiliza el explosivo para enviar al mago de vuelta a su deprimente castillo.

programme.title: El Hombre De La Luna
programme.desc: Cansado y harto de que no le aprecien, el Hombre de la Luna deja su trabajo y se retira en la Tierra, en la Aldea Pitufa. La ausencia de la luna en cuarto creciente desata el caos en las costumbres de los Pitufos, y Madre Naturaleza y Padre Tiempo tambien se ven arrastrados por el embrollo...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Poeta y Pintor se sienten poco valorados y huyen a una isla tormentosa sin saber que Gargamel los sigue hasta alli.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Nadie le cree al Abuelo Pitufo cuando habla de junglas y sabanas lejanas, repletas de gatos salvajes gigantes, caballos a rayas, comedores de hojas de cuello largo y extranas tribus... Tan solo algunos Pitufitos dan cierto credito a sus historias. Pero, cuando Abuelo Pitufo escucha en el bosque el sonido del tambor real magico, un instrumento capaz de domar bestias salvajes, se lanza a la aventura para demostrar que no es un contador de historias al que el cerebro le juega malas pasadas.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Natural y Travieso roban la formula de Gargamel para hacer otro Pitufo - otra pitufa para acompanar a Pitufina. Asi pues, crean a Sassette, que crea problemas por doquier. Haciendo uso de su pocion, Papa Pitufo convierte la malvada creacion de Gargamel en una simpatica Sassette.

programme.title: A Todas Las Criaturas Grandes Y Pequenas
programme.desc: Pitufo Natural esta convencido de que puede ayudar a todas las criaturas con sus dones curativos, incluso al malvado Azrael, cuya pata queda atrapada en una trampa. El gato se cura y, a pesar de que tiene la tentacion de quedarse con los Pitufos, regresa con Gargamel, pero conduce a su dueno hacia un lugar alejado de la Aldea Pitufa.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Los Pitufos hambrientos descubren una cueva en donde se encuentra oculta comida congelada custodiada por un trol tambien congelado quien fue encarcelado debido a su avaricia por un diamante magico. Mientras los Pitufos descongelan la cueva Gargamel roba la comida, pero el diamante magico lo transforma en una masa helada y el trol liberado ayuda gustosamente a los Pitufos a cargar la comida de regreso a su aldea.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Pitufo Filosofo y Bebe Pitufo mezclan las formulas de Papa Pitufo con consecuencias desastrosas, dejandoles a merced de un ejercito de hambrientas langostas que Gargamel ha soltado en el bosque.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Las provisiones de comida de los Pitufos para el invierno se estropea y preparan un viaje hasta un lejano castillo en el que pueden refugiarse. Al principio, creen que el castillo esta embrujado, pero tras descubrir que solo se trata de un grupo de ratas, el propietario del castillo les obsequia comida en abundancia para el largo invierno.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Fortachon descubre a un caballero que lo ayuda a combatir a un Dragon, pero este huye y deja a Fortachon defendiendo a los Pitufos.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Los Pitufos aman las trufas y las trufas son de los Trolls. No sera nada facil que los pitufitos azules tengan un banquete.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Papa Pitufo recuerda las emocionantes aventuras de Sonador en el mar, con tortugas, ballenas, islas desiertas...y piratas!

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.sub-title: Viaje Al Pitufo De La Tierra
programme.desc: El invierno ha llegado a la Aldea Pitufa. Y los pequenos Pitufos estan helados de frio. ¿Pero que esta haciendo Pitufo Torpe con esa extrana roca que ha descubierto? ¿Y por que esta tan entusiasmado Pitufo Minero con su nuevo descubrimiento? Nadie entiende a que se debe tanto revuelo por una simple nueva roca para la coleccion de Pitufo Torpe... Al adentrarse bajo tierra, los Pitufos encontraran peligros y sorpresas.

programme.title: El Bebe Pitufo
programme.desc: Gargamel se transforma en un Bebe Pitufo, para ser adoptado por los Pitufos. Causa un completo caos en la Aldea de los Pitufos cuando intenta hacerlos volar por los aires con una bomba. Papa Pitufo descubre su malvado plan y utiliza el explosivo para enviar al mago de vuelta a su deprimente castillo.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Pitufo Fortachon se disfraza de Pitufina para atraer a Piltkin, el gnomo que se ha enamorado de ella, y alejarlo de la Aldea Pitufa. Excavan bajo tierra y conocen a una gnoma que se enamora de Piltkin, quien se olvida de Pitufina y pasa a tener ojos solo para su nueva conquista.

programme.title: La Formula Aniquiladora
programme.desc: Existe una palabra magica aterradora. Cuando pronuncias esa palabra hacia algo o alguien, ¡haces que se desvanezca en la nada! ¿Podran los Pitufos anular su malvado poder antes de que Gargamel se apropie de ella?

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Todos los Pitufos quieren un poema escrito para cada uno de ellos. Pitufo Poeta se siente superado por la presion y decide huir en busca de inspiracion. El rey Fiera Bestia captura a Pitufo Poeta y lo obliga a escribir un poema para animar a su hija. Pitufo Poeta descubre que la motivacion debe nacer del corazon, y nunca de la obligacion.

programme.title: La Desgracia De Gargamel
programme.desc: Gargamel, el malvado e incompetente mago, intenta enganar a la gitana Esmeralda para que le de una formula para atrapar a los Pitufos. Por supuesto, la gitana demuestra ser mucho mas lista que Gargamel, y los Pitufos aun mas.

programme.title: El Libro De Bromas De Bromista
programme.desc: Las cajas sorpresa de Pitufo Bromista ya no resultan divertidas para los demas Pitufos. Pitufo Bromista busca nuevas ideas en su «Gran libro de las bromas», pero esas ideas son aun peor recibidas en la aldea. Y entonces, Gargamel llega con algunas bromas de su propia cosecha...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Pitufo Perezoso suena que esta en la Isla Paraiso y libre de todo el trabajo que Papa Pitufo le impone. Su fantasia se vuelve una pesadilla que lo hace volver a trabajar nuevamente con afan.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Otra estupenda produccion del teatro de los Pitufos basada en los personajes de Alejandro Dumas. Incluye algunas lineas de Romeo y Julieta. Una obra maestra de la escena.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: El malvado brujo Gargamel pide al mago Balthazar una receta para capturar a los pitufos. Implica secuestrar a la Madre Naturaleza para impedir la llegada de la Primavera. Por suerte, los pitufos salvan la situacion.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: El malvado primo del Rey, Malcolm, lo ha convertido en un ciervo negro para poder acabar con el y ponerle en su sala de trofeos. Los Pitufos iran a ayudar a su amigo y, tras devolver al Rey a su verdadera forma, Malcom acabara preso dentro del cuerpo del ciervo negro.

programme.title: El Mal Genio
programme.desc: Los Pitufos encuentran un Genio en una lampara que se niega a concederles sus deseos sin la palabra magica.

programme.title: Superpitufo
programme.desc: Giganton roba el suministro de alimentos de invierno y de los Pitufos y Pitufo Filosofo prepara una de las pociones de fortaleza de Papa Pitufo para que pueda luchar contra el codicioso gigante. La super formula desaparece, pero Papa Pitufo hace un cambio rapido, cambia la comida por piedras y Giganton sale perdiendo.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Creyendo que Bebe Pitufo es un duende, dos cazadores furtivos lo secuestran e intentan que el pequeno les diga donde ha escondido la olla de oro. Papa Pitufo organiza a todos para atacar a los villanos con tartas de pitufrutas y lograr que Bebe Pitufo pueda escapar.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Pitufo Tontin, al querer ser el mas popular, roba uno de los hechizos de Gargamel, pero no lo usa bien y acaba convirtiendose en un dragon. Ahora tendran que juntarse todos los Pitufos junto con Papa Pitufo para colarse en el castillo de Gargamel y encontrar el antidoto que hara que Pitufo Tontin vuelva a su forma normal.

programme.title: Pitufos Y Solo Pitufos
programme.desc: El malvado mago Gargamel ha conseguido capturar a Pitufina. Ahora, se dispone a administrarle un suero de la verdad para descubrir todos los secretos de Papa Pitufo... pero Gargamel comete un gran error y le da a Pitufina una formula de las mentiras.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: El chico del bosque y Laconia, la elfa muda y sorda, preguntan a Papa Pitufo que celebre su boda. Mientras los Pitufos preparan la fiesta bajo las ordenes de Pitufina, Gargamel hace acto de presencia.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.sub-title: La Primera Navidad De Bebe Pitufo
programme.desc: La ilusion de Navidad se ve frustrada cuando Chlorhydris hechiza a San Nicolas para que no pueda repartir felicidad en Navidad. Afortunadamente, Papa Pitufo y los demas pitufos consiguen romper el hechizo y devolver la Navidad a su bosque.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: La produccion teatral de los Pitufos "Pitufo Robin" se convierte en realidad con un actor real del legendario heroe.

programme.title: Pitufos Helados
programme.desc: El invierno ha llegado y los Pitufos estan a punto de sucumbir al intenso frio. ¿Podra Pitufo Rastreador encontrar el remedio sin caer en las garras de Gargamel?

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Gargamel y Baltasar se ponen a los mandos de un Robotin gigante para obligar al rey Gerard a que les entregue a Pitufo Robotin. Cuando el Robotin esta a punto de destruir el castillo, Giganton, el nuevo, enorme y extrano amigo de Pitufo Robotin, vence al Robotin. Pitufo Robotin sufre danos durante la batalla, pero Pitufo Carpintero lo arregla y le implanta una caja de voz que le permite decir «¡Hola!».

programme.title: El Amigo Mas Pitufo
programme.desc: Pitufo Filosofo tenia un amigo: Pitufo Torpe. Pero el pobre Pitufo Torpe es tan... bueno, torpe, que Pitufo Filosofo no quiere volverle a ver. Asi que ahora no queda nadie dispuesto a escucharle. Quiza Buddy, el apuesto diablillo que ha conocido por casualidad cerca del gran roble, pueda convertirse en amigo de Pitufo Filosofo...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Genio inventa una maquina que hara todo el trabajo de cosechar y preparar la comido de los Pitufos. Pero esta milagrosa invencion tiene sus bemoles.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Cuando el Pitufo Filosofo pierde sus gafas deja caer las cosas, tropieza con los objetos, y se convierte en tan patoso como el Pitufo Tontin, que ahora tiene que leer a Filosofo y ayudarle a manejarse. Esta experiencia hace que Filosofo se sienta culpable por la forma en la que siempre se ha burlado de Tontin. Una vez que recibe un nuevo par de gafas, le trata con mas respeto.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.sub-title: La Primera Palabra De Bebe Pitufo
programme.desc: Los Pitufitos liberan a los Pitufos de las garras de Gargamel justo a tiempo para llevar a Bebe Pitufo a la ceremonia de su primera palabra. Bebe Pitufo pronuncia la palabra «Gargamel». Papa Pitufo afirma que esa palabra indica que Bebe Pitufo se convertira un dia en un gran lider, ya que significa que es consciente de los peligros de la vida.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: El malvado primo del Rey, Malcolm, lo ha convertido en un ciervo negro para poder acabar con el y ponerle en su sala de trofeos. Los Pitufos iran a ayudar a su amigo y, tras devolver al Rey a su verdadera forma, Malcom acabara preso dentro del cuerpo del ciervo negro.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Cada manana, los duendecillos del agua depositan rocio sobre las hojas del bosque. No imaginas todo lo que ocurrira cuando Pitufo Miedoso se transforme con la varita magica que crea las gotas de rocio...

programme.title: Lenguaje De Senas
programme.desc: Los Pitufos conocen a un elfo del bosque, que les ensena la lengua de signos despues de que Gargamel les administre una pocion de enmudecimiento.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: El malvado mago Gargamel ha conseguido unos huevos magicos de cristal citoplasmico que le permitiran intercambiar su cuerpo con el de Papa Pitufo. ¿Que otro plan mejor que ese podria haber? Una vez que este en el cuerpo de Papa Pitufo, llevara a todos los Pitufos hasta su caldero. Pero, por juegos del destino, Gargamel se transforma en Perro, el perro de los Pitufos...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: En un esfuerzo por conseguir que Papa Pitufo tenga algo de tranquilidad, Pitufo Filosofo usa uno de los hechizos de Papa Pitufo para crear una barrera de sonido magica alrededor de la aldea. Papa Pitufo no es capaz de deshacer el hechizo y envia a los Pitufitos, que han quedado atrapados fuera de la aldea, a un hacedor de ruidos. Bebe Pitufo se lleva una botella de ruido de casa del hacedor de ruidos, y asi consiguen romper la barrera.

programme.title: La Aguja Magica De Pitufo Sastre
programme.desc: Pitufo Sastre tiene que crear un conjunto para cada Pitufo antes del desfile de moda de otono. Pitufo Filosofo quiere ayudarle y, usando el libro de magia de Papa Pitufo, conjura una aguja magica que cose diez veces mas rapido que un sastre... ¿Pero es eso algo realmente bueno?

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: El Dia de los Inocentes Pitufo resulta no ser tan divertido cuando Gargamel se pone un disfraz de Pitufoarbusto para capturar al pequeno Pitufo Feliz. Papa Pitufo pide ayuda a Pitufopluma para que llame a los pajaros y ataquen al falso arbusto.

programme.title: Los Amigos De Sonador
programme.desc: Cuando Pitufo Sonador decide visitar a sus amigos, los Tufos, Papa Pitufo crea una pocion para transformar a los Pitufos en criaturas de aspecto alienigena. Sin embargo, los efectos de la pocion desaparecen demasiado pronto y Pitufo Sonador tiene que enfrentarse a la realidad de que los Tufos no existen. Esta triste hasta que llega un alienigena de verdad para devolver a Pitufo Sonador su carta, ya que la recibio por error.

programme.title: La Reina Pitufina
programme.desc: Pitufina se convierte en reina por un dia en su cumpleanos. Sin embargo, la situacion se descontrola cuando Padre Tiempo se queda dormido y no cumple su cometido de terminar los dias. Los animos comienzan a calentarse entre los Pitufos, que estan cansados de trabajar. Papa Pitufo acude a despertar a Padre Tiempo y trae de vuelta la paz a la tierra de los Pitufos.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Los Pitufos van al rescate de dos ninos y su abuelo, cuando un misterioso extranjero aparece haciendo que su trineo se rompa en pedazos. Al llamar a la puerta de Gargamel en busca de ayuda, no se dan cuenta de que estan poniendo en peligro sus vidas y la de los Pitufos...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.sub-title: Pitufo Marco Y Los Piratas Pimienta
programme.desc: Los Pitufos navegan para salvar a Marco, que ha sido capturado por el Capitan Pedro Pimienta. Marina y un delfin acaban liberando a Marco.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Un duende maligno le pone unos zapatos magicos a Pitufina, que no puede dejar de bailar, con la intencion de que le prometa que se casara con el. Todos sus pequenos amigos acuden a rescatarla y Papa Pitufo consigue ponerle los zapatos magicos al duende, obligandole a bailar hasta que se hace de noche.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Pitufo Deshollinador se encarga de limpiar las chimeneas y no es precisamente el habitante mas popular de la Aldea Pitufa. Es bastante desalinado, y las nubes de hollin que suelta no contribuyen a aumentar su popularidad. Unicamente los Pitufitos le consideran una excelente compania, ya que es el unico Pitufo que puede ensuciarse sin que le rinan. Sin embargo, el entusiasmo de los Pitufitos por Pitufo Deshollinador pone en peligro la aldea.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Pitufina promete a Madre Naturaleza que, si crea una rosa azul, nunca la cortara. Pero, cuando la rosa blanca se vuelve azul, Pitufina pasa a ser de color blanco. Lo unico que Pitufina puede hacer para volver a ser azul es cortar la rosa. Corta la rosa a reganadientes, lo que devuelve la naturaleza a la normalidad, y aprende que no siempre se pueden mantener las promesas.

programme.title: Power & Sport S1 - "Water - Kevin Langeree"
programme.desc: Big Air kiteboarder Kevin Langeree shows some extreme kitesurfing on the waters of Noordwijk and Tarifa.

programme.title: Power & Sport S1 - "Wheels - Lutz Eicholz"
programme.desc: Lutz Eicholz descends the Austrian Alps with his unicycle.

programme.title: Street Art Challenge S1 - "St. Petersburg"
programme.desc: English and South American street artists pair up to take on an epic challenge in the world's biggest country, Russia. The men have to finish a complete circus.

programme.title: Street Art Challenge S1 - "Athens"
programme.desc: Two American street artists try to turn a school into a piece of art. Seems impossible, but this duo turns out to be a real American Dream Team.

programme.title: Close Proximity S1 - "Morgan Hill"
programme.desc: After a loss against Formula Drift newcomer Faruk Kugay in Atlanta, Matt is back in Morgan Hill, cleaning up the Drift Cave before heading to Orlando.

programme.title: Close Proximity S1 - "Orlando"
programme.desc: Following a disappointing 12th place finish in the Formula Drift series stop in Orlando, drift car driver Matt Field prepares for the next stop: Wall Speedway.

programme.title: Close Proximity S1 - "Long Break"
programme.desc: After a week-long break, Matt Field and his crew are refreshed and ready for their next stop in Montreal, Canada.

programme.title: 7 Days S1 - "Day 3"
programme.desc: Kevin leaves civilization behind in Suriname, while thousands of kilometers away, Jalou has to go literally through the trees in an Australian forest.

programme.title: 7 Days S1 - "Day 4"
programme.desc: Jalou and Kevin travel to far colder places to challenge each other in an ice climbing competition.

programme.title: Graveyard Carz S17 - "A Reynolds ‘Cuda Reunion"
programme.desc: When Tony D’Agostino makes another trip to the west coast, Mark Worman takes the opportunity to revisit the Brothers Car Collection in Salem, Oregon to do a deep dive on a 1971 Hemi ’Cuda that shares history with the Sandwich Man himself.

programme.title: Graveyard Carz S17 - "One for the Road Movie"
programme.desc: The Vanishing Point Challenger has not disappeared from view. After years of gathering rust in the Graveyard, this 1970 Alpine White Challenger R/T tribute car has been cleaned up, and has received most of its sheet metal.

programme.title: Graveyard Carz S17 - "This is a Crack Up!"
programme.desc: The team takes on the biggest engine challenge of their lives! A numbers matching 383 for a 1971 ‘Cuda, that has multiple, massive, freeze cracks in the block. Mark puts a local shop to the test, as they attempt to save an engine.

programme.title: Graveyard Carz S17 - "The Thunder from Down Under"
programme.desc: When the local junkyard closes its doors, Mark and Dougie have to rescue an old friend from the earliest days of Graveyard Carz. But their journey appears to be cursed by a sudden increase in thunder and lightning.

programme.title: Yoga For All
programme.desc: Your Day 4 practice provides you the opportunity to lean in when you feel discomfort to embrace the process of finding ease. Discover layers of your home practice as we look at our patterns and continue to build a dynamic vocabulary that serves.

programme.title: Deep Relaxation with Tracee Stanley
programme.desc: In this final practice we allow for more spaciousness, so give yourself ample time for the 30-minute practice and at least 5 minutes of journaling afterward. Make sure that you don't have to rush off anywhere right after so that you can enjoy the feeling of peace and integration throughout your body

programme.title: Deep Relaxation with Tracee Stanley
programme.desc: Move beyond the mind and connect with a deeper part of yourself. Experiment and let go and explore your true nature to create a new way of being in the world.

programme.title: The Nature of Reality
programme.sub-title: The Nature of Reality: Union with Yourself
programme.desc: The essential nature of the physical world is that it's not physical. The essential nature of the material world is that it's not material. As Rumi says, “We come spinning out of nothingness scattering stars like dust.”

programme.title: The Nature of Reality
programme.sub-title: The Nature of Reality: The Science of Reality
programme.desc: What is real? How do we know it's real, and how does that deeper understanding of reality help us fulfill our dreams, desires, and intentions? So let's go for it.

programme.title: Vinyasa for Life
programme.sub-title: Vinyasa for Life: Easing into Back Bending
programme.desc: Establish long term success for your practice by learning about one of the most crucial body parts in yoga—your spine. In this class Schuyler teaches you how to backbend safely, followed by three practical applications. Class ends with a soothing restorative posture. Body awareness never felt so good.

programme.title: Yoga For All
programme.desc: Your Day 1 practice offers an invitation to slow down and take stock.

programme.title: Break Out of the Addiction Frequency
programme.sub-title: Section 1: The Addiction Frequency & The Power of Breath
programme.desc: Breathing is the single most important thing we do. Addiction is characterized by a sense of lack, of missing something. And when you breathe poorly, like when anxious or angry, you’re caught up in your head and aren’t breathing well and that sends a signal to your body that perpetuates the addiction frequency. Deep, long breathing is how we interrupt this pattern.

programme.title: Hacking Your Healthcare

programme.desc: Today, we talk about a revolutionary approach to health called Functional Medicine, and how you can have a healthy doctor-patient relationship.

programme.title: Relationships with Marianne Williamson
programme.sub-title: Relationships: Relationships and Your Spiritual Journey
programme.desc: Today's lesson is a bit of a reality check, as we'll begin to question the current way we look at relationships, romantic or not. How we see ourselves and our relationship to God influences our view of our relationships with other people. Today we're going to examine that view from a place of love.

programme.desc: In this course, Anita Moorjani guides you toward loving yourself as if your life depends on it – because it does! When love (rather than fear) determines your life, you will recognize what is truly important for you to be happy and healthy.

programme.desc: As humans, we are constantly struggling between the poles of what we think we want and what is. When we lose touch with the truth of what is, we create and compound our suffering. What narratives are you constructing? Are they in conflict with the truth of the situation? Are you struggling with what is?
